{"tid":1525250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荔景站職員出賣香港人！引狗入黎拉乘客！","createTime":"2019-08-31T20:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:51:40.000Z","uid":14993,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"63c0bb2c6ce5223b5eb657d3f98a07511d9972d8","tid":1525250,"uid":14993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:58:06.000Z","msg":"利申先，我係代朋友開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下文字係佢轉述比我嘅：<br />\n<br />\n頭先十一點幾荃灣線突然停左，成班喺荔景嘅乘客們想返屋企，擔心又會出現太子站黑警無差別攻擊既狀況，<br />\n所以乘客們就包圍月台control room，<br />\n叫黃衫友出黎回應點解荔景去荃灣方向都唔行駛同要求解決方案，例如接駁巴士之類。<br />\n條仆街（圖左）一開始都唔理，淨係做手勢叫大家冷靜，一邊用對講機講野，<br />\n搞左成十幾分鐘，大家應承唔會打佢，淨係想要交代，佢先喺另一個仆街（圖右）陪同下出黎諗住走。<br />\n佢話佢都唔知咩事，我地就要求見站長，<br />\n呢兩個黃衫叫我地等等，<br />\n仲話帶我地落去下層近閘口位搵站長。<br />\n跟住大家落到去，<br />\n一等就等左十幾分鐘，<br />\n（中間乘客們仲同返兩個仆街講唔好意思語氣重左，圖左仆街仲話明大家想返屋企，佢都係打份工，好似大和解左咁），<br />\n突然三十個拎盾既防暴衝左入地鐵站！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家嚇到四散，入面有c9有老人家！ <br />\n我地果刻冇人帶gear, 冇人有用過武力！ <br />\n好地地咁想要解決方案，<br />\n黨鐵職員扮友善，淨淨雞引清兵入關！ <br />\n<br />\n睇返自己live段片右手邊個職員叫羅振輝，<br />\n左手邊果個話唔小心跌左塊名牌入衫袋，麻煩手足幫手了解下佢係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zdE8FOi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzdE8FOi.jpg&h=c4ee07d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係咁，朋友覺得好唔忿氣點解明明咩都冇做都會有成班防暴衝入黎，所以叫我開po"},{"pid":"3a118ff74e27a5417d3c52748d51d89f41037541","tid":1525250,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:00:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【國際路線】全世界印同舉依款標語</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifcqnMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifcqnMz.png&h=19bda72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/taez0yf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftaez0yf.png&h=868ecca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttTpDjV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttTpDjV.png&h=ada7f3ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbff327e1d1a26e38891351aa17384b2dd4439e9","tid":1525250,"uid":201816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:01:27.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<br />\n黨鐵垃圾職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf933b2b5484b5d4c805271b070877381165d19","tid":1525250,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:04:56.000Z","msg":"最尾有無啦人"},{"pid":"99d07137e6fbd7e01e0d99145d960c4bed97aa7a","tid":1525250,"uid":14993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2cf933b2b5484b5d4c805271b070877381165d19","tid":1525250,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:04:56.000Z","msg":"最尾有無啦人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:07:19.000Z","msg":"佢瞓左 聽日問，不過我估就冇，大家一見防爆都嚇到雞飛狗走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbde2c4132503dc78406d8f07e46e1fc048de234","tid":1525250,"uid":14993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:07:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07d522267b76ea93dfef9ad808736c9708c60237","tid":1525250,"uid":14993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b166636f0a43aa5fdaf203cef28983074bf870","tid":1525250,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:07:55.000Z","msg":"黨<br />\n鐵<br />\n不<br />\n無<br />\n辜"},{"pid":"9127d15da44a0420a82ba475e17a76ccb48700c0","tid":1525250,"uid":14993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T21:10:23.000Z","msg":"黨鐵正仆街"},{"pid":"199b622f70b0db303c128ef2ae5cadaad2ada8e1","tid":1525250,"uid":14993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score